		<p>Search publications on <a href="http://inspirebeta.net/search?p=FIND+EA+PRITCHARD%2C+JONATHAN+R+OR+PRITCHARD%2C+JONATHAN+OR+PRITCHARD%2C+J+R">SPIRES</a>, <a 
